data.description: OWNED SOLAR!!! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home your own! Tastefully renovated to create a modern and inviting living space perfect for creating lasting memories. Open concept floor plan with a ton of space! Breakfast bar allows for causal dining, while the dining area is ideal for hosting formal meals. 5 bedrooms, generously sized! Updated bathrooms with modern fixtures and finishes. Outside you'll discover a true oasis, covered patio, sparkling pool and lush landscaping that provides the perfect space for entertaining! Additional garage/ carport allowing for convenient parking and storage space. Schedule your showing today!
